        <h3>Beverly Hills hotel (200 rooms), Speed Queen Quantum SC60 60 lb capacity</h3>
        <p>Hotel laundry room. Drain pump degraded plus inlet valve stuck closed (hard water scale). Single-visit replacement to minimize downtime, hotel cycled to backup machine during 90-minute repair. Total: $120 plus $440 drain pump plus $280 inlet valve = $720.</p>
      </div>
