      </div>
      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>Long Beach hospital, Continental Girbau EH075 75 lb high-extract</h3>
        <p>Hospital linen. Drive belt frayed plus front bearing showing wear (high-extract earlier-life bearing, year 7 unit). Replaced belt, replaced front bearing assembly, balanced drum. Total: $120 plus $640 parts plus $640 labor = $1,400.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>West Hollywood restaurant chain, Maytag Commercial 40 lb capacity</h3>
        <p>Restaurant uniform laundry. Door interlock switch failed plus boot seal showed cracking. Quick parts swap, total under 90 minutes. Total: $120 plus $200 interlock plus $160 boot seal = $480.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

